column4: A monthly official tournament event sponsored by the WNA!{=br}Earn fabulous rewards, like badges for each tournament and Jala!{=br}Be sure to join in and aim for the top in the WNA Tours!{=br}{=br}*Tournament rankings are calculated separately from normal rankings. {=br}*Tournament rewards will be sent to your in-game mailbox after the tournament rankings have been finalized.

The following actions are prohibited during the tournament. {=br}If we confirm the occurrence of any of the following acts,{=br}your tournament entry and prizes may be forfeited. {=br}・Confirmation of falsified data and unauthorized operations{=br}・Working with other users to manipulate battle outcomes{=br}・The use of offensive player names and other acts of harassment, etc.{=br}that impede with gameplay{=br}・Any other acts that are determined to be interfering with the tournament{=br}If you exit the matching lobby repeatedly,{=br}it will be considered an act of harassment and you may be temporarily restricted from matching. {=br}
